<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Elevated error rates for Route 53>
We are currently experiencing elevated error rates for the Route 53 Management Console. API and DNS queries are all being answered normally.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Elevated error rates for Route 53 Management Console>
We have identified the root cause for the elevated error rates on the Route 53 Management Console and are starting to see recovery. Route 53 API calls and DNS resolution continue to operate normally.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Elevated error rates for Route 53 Management Console>
Between 7:49 PM and 8:45 PM PST the Route 53 Management Console was experiencing elevated error rates. The issue has been resolved and the Route 53 Management Console is now operating normally. During this entire time period the Route 53 API and DNS resolution continued to function normally.
